com.tomtom.speedtools.tracer

Class Trace

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.speedtools.tracer.Trace
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MongoDBTrace

    public class Trace
extends Object
    Class to store a single logging event. A Trace can contain any (serializable) object, or a class which extends SimpleTraceEvent.

        An event is specific for an 'owning class'. The event is type-safe and its type is defined by the 'eventInterface'.
        Parameters:
        clazz - Class throwing the event.
        tracer - Type-safe event interface.
        method - Method throwing the event.
        time - Event time.
        args - Additional arguments passed with the method.
